# admin-app Rules

- Keep admin-app focused on map configuration management workflows.
- Do not move map rendering concerns into `packages/map-ui-lib`.
- Reuse shared config/schema contracts from the library package.
- Keep edits aligned with Config -> Zod -> Zustand -> App -> URL expectations.

Required references:

- `.claude/skills/project-conventions/SKILL.md`
- `.claude/skills/extend-map-config/SKILL.md`
- `.agent/workflows/development.md`
